AT least 30 people have died and a further 100 been
injured in 10 separate road accidents in the past 24 hours.In the most serious accident, 18 died when a truck, a bus
and a taxi collided outside Machadorp , Mpumalanga. The accident happened about
7am.Also early this morning, four people burnt to death in
Newcastle, KZN when their BMW burst into flames after colliding with another
